Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底要帶我們去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人的根據地居然就在司令部的地下深處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 不光是大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊自身也脫不了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也並不全是壞消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我的身體？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他說「你不是我的靈魂 所以不能跟你走」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體還在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 我們更接近目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 為什麼那個白黑貓會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那個豆丁女在裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 你快點把短褲穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}愚者的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把那樣的傢伙也帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的事情交給拉斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯是大總統金格·布拉德雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了各種各樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利曹長是南部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾蔓准尉是北部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普雷達少尉被貶到了西部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克愛中尉似乎成了大總統專用輔佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是表面上的人質嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這個屋子裡只有我們和大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器只有一把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣 也有贏的自信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs60\fad(0,200)}（咳）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳 咳咳 咳咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前 我們住院的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來看過我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被你騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「別插手 把軍隊內部全部都當作是敵人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該是這麼命令你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對我們來說是非常珍貴的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要知道多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在時間到來之前乖乖待著就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 不會對你們怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個時間到來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們人柱以外的一般人會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了你不必知道多餘的事情 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 什麼鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了恢復原來的身體 選擇成為軍隊的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家鍊金術師制度本身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計就是為了選出人柱的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果之後還要再被你們利用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不如辭掉國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走狗的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被沾得都是血了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會讓它失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這件事告訴其他的術師們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩叫什麼名字來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 溫莉·洛克貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利塞布爾出生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們的青梅竹馬 對你們來說她和家人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術不錯的機械鎧技師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在拉修巴雷工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時被客人和同伴稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠實的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許對她出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對周圍的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說不需要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就捨棄掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話 我們都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這基礎上 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以往一樣我們處於你們的監視下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對地 讓我們繼續恢復身體的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續我們的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不幹多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古大佐準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會說辭職之類的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 即使成為家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法忍受成為一隻敗犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為了我的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫去軍服或者捨棄這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都無法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能問你一個問題嗎 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼問題？大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死休斯的是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.65,0:07:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說只問一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 阿爾馮斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭頂上…劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我點零錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別多問了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是路邊的混混嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 大佐 之後再向你匯報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女性約好的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站著個肌肉鬍鬚不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪個男人會有好臉色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍克愛中尉 從洗手間回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受阿姆斯壯少佐的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換崗了一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位說了不論發生什麼都不要逃避的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候別和我說還是逃跑比較好哦 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把機械鎧弄壞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧 還精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒出什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒被奇怪的人跟蹤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為愛德很少打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次居然還關心起我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙 妳以為我多麼地…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到電話我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真的不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之暫時沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼拚命才會成為被攻擊的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受你的朋友所托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是清的語言嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 不會讀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是交給等著這傢伙的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會想之後跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後殺了那個女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會做這種偷偷摸摸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我沒有和女人打架的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的信條就是不說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有即使讓這個國家衰退也要發起內亂的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道外面的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡邏的人暫時不會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我是醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給你療傷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊修瓦爾人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這額頭的傷疤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你就是斯卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是參加了殲滅伊修瓦爾的鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜養一段時間就會好起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自增加患者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床和沙發被佔據了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始我在哪裡睡才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}（再說 家裡居然多住兩個人…）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 妳必須躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 少主沒有和你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡有他的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢者之…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是得到了賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們一族就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 得馬上回國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個消息告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沉默？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道少主發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 阿爾馮斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體的狀況怎麼樣 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是拉斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:14:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎 這個身體是清的皇子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得到成為皇帝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己接受了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的王是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被這個皇子這麼問過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王是為了人民而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說 沒有人民就沒有王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終還不是為了欲望而失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 如果一有空隙就準備侵佔我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是虎視眈眈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連怪物也想吞下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類欲望到底有多強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統是人造人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:15:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩想為我國弱小的人民而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大批的人也這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信任著軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入了軍籍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 這個軍隊卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辭去軍隊的工作如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的性格 留下也只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰鬥是錯誤的 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想違背軍令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 去叫替補的國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊修瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩從戰鬥中逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的做法是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我應該為了糾正這種錯誤而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有一天不對扭曲的信念和一直逃避的自己感到可恥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在軍隊再次成為了戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩怎麼能一個人夾著尾巴逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐今後打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和大總統說 我還有野心所以不會辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統自己把自己是人造人的事情告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在暗示 即使打倒我 還有在後面操縱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被他試了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很光榮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你這麼從容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 在和名叫拉斯多的人造人戰鬥的時候也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱作「兵器 怪物」的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真正的怪物戰鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能夠切身感受到自己只是個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主自願接受了賢者之石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 如果我們阻止他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是生氣自己沒能盡到護衛的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主還在那個叫古利德的傢伙裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要手臂 現在就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…說要現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我介紹個機械鎧技師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡快介紹給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那之前得積蓄體力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向諾克斯醫生拿飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以起來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是叫張梅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是姚家的看門狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳是張家的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是我 第17皇女 張梅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到這個國家 就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是長生不老
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會交給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳無法達到目的的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.14,0:18:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要對別人國家的事情插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我受傷了 別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那句台詞 我原封不動還給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人就乖乖躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對別人國家的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我管妳什麼國家的事情 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人萬國共通 都是病人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們想再弄亂我的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.92,0:18:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從醫生的家裡傳出未知的病原體全員死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是亂得一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有誰來收拾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是家人的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離別的老婆和兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼處理我的東西都是我的自由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾好了就喝杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能來真是幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也是這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.29,0:19:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好在完全沒轍的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 術可以用了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣修復就全部完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是國家鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那些術師的等級完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實上午的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓附近的鍊金術師來幫忙修復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起那些傢伙真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信滿滿地進入現場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了卻說無法用鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們在地下的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩維說的話真的可以相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是沒有肉體和精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純粹的能量體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 要考慮之後的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我和阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的術師也無法使用鍊金術了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個豆丁女和斯卡能夠使用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們不同的鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能打聽出它的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許不使用賢者之石也能奪回阿爾的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個鬍鬚男對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要去還給中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被迫協助他們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去了大量伊修瓦爾人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被迫協助參與可能會出現更多犧牲者的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要以死來報一箭之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.34,0:23:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來就像是神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有聽說伊修瓦爾的全部事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在那塊土地上做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部說出來 馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.92,0:23:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這個右手還沒有破壞你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是無休止的蹂躪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地滲入了鮮紅的血
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.63,0:24:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大氣中彌漫著焦肉的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不祥的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.65,0:24:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第30話 伊修瓦爾殲滅戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.29,0:24:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只剩一人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要闡述真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}心神不定  因為我由於不決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:16.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}輕微的顫抖著  control過了還在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}太陽也好  運氣（月亮）也罷  完全與我無緣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:21.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}「只有硬上了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我這樣勸說自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:30.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}情況很糟糕  臨陣逃脫又沒毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}雖然前途未卜  也只能靠膽量獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:37.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}壓制著衝動  尋找敵我之間的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur4}唯一需要的是勝利的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:43.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}能嘗下勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}或者喝下滿腔的苦水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}是的  一切都是二擇其一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.70,0:00:55.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}好想操縱命運的輪盤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:01:00.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}絕好的黃金時間  親自把握機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}擺出一副撲克臉  設下陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:09.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}把敵人引入幻想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:16.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無盡的pressure game  跨越過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.14,0:01:20.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}為了跨越榮耀的borderline
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:24.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}How many？  我需要支付多少代價？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:29.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}到底捨不得放棄哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:38.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,250)\blur2}一輪又一輪後依然想在此相見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:45.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}為了不再走散而緊緊牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:48.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}談話直到日出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}牽手直到日落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:56.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2\i1}就這樣明天後天也一直這樣形影不離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:01.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}寂寞的看著街上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:06.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一個人是無法找到溫暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:11.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)\blur2}第一次知道愛原來可以如此堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:17.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\blur2}那是在與你相遇之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:23.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一輪又一輪後依然想在此相見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:28.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了不再走散而緊緊牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:33.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為一個人無法入睡  也無法做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:39.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在不安無法到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:44.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}即使是沒有星星的夜晚也要繼續將其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:47.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}和你在一起的話能到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:50.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}一個人無法走過的道路  如果是兩個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\i1}就可以哼著歌走過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.09,0:22:56.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2\i1}只要有你在就很幸福


